X-pgp-sig mail and news header utility for emacs
	
x-pgp-sig header utility for emacs.
it can insert/verify pgp signatures in the x-pgp-sig: mail/news header.
x-pgp-sig.el is for mh(mh-e, mew and so on), gnus, semi-gnus, wl(wanderlust)
vm, cmail etc... (mua on emacs).

english documentation is not available, only japanese.